120
00:13:27,060 --> 00:13:35,685
[SPEAKER_20]: Take the 33% vacancy rate in the luxury apartments in the Seaport District and the uninhabited biotech buildings in Boston and Cambridge built in the last decade.

121
00:13:36,185 --> 00:13:38,367
[SPEAKER_20]: If we build it, they may not come.

122
00:13:39,163 --> 00:13:43,325
[SPEAKER_20]: That might be okay for developers, but it must not be okay for our city.

123
00:13:43,845 --> 00:13:52,530
[SPEAKER_20]: We must only build for what there is a demonstrated need and demand for using available actionable data with lots and lots of cooling green space.

